          {
            "id": "rule_1",
            "type": "rule",
            "content": {
              "text": "**expo-audio-stream** is a comprehensive audio processing monorepo for React Native and Expo applications. It provides real-time audio recording, analysis, visualization, and AI-powered processing capabilities across iOS, Android, and web platforms.",
              "originalHeader": "Repository Overview"
            },
            "metadata": {
              "strength": "SHOULD",
              "format": "Paragraph",
              "line_start": 6,
              "line_end": 6
            }
          },
          {
            "id": "rule_2",
            "type": "rule",
            "content": {
              "text": "### Core Packages\n- **`@siteed/expo-audio-studio`** - Main audio processing library with dual-stream recording, device management, and format conversion\n- **`@siteed/expo-audio-ui`** - React Native Skia-based audio visualization components (waveforms, spectrograms)\n- **`@siteed/react-native-essentia`** - Advanced audio analysis using Essentia (feature extraction, classification)\n- **`@siteed/sherpa-onnx.rn`** - Speech-to-text and text-to-speech capabilities (development)",
              "originalHeader": "Repository Overview"
            },
            "metadata": {
              "strength": "SHOULD",
              "format": "Paragraph",
              "line_start": 8,
              "line_end": 13
            }
          },
          {
            "id": "rule_3",
            "type": "rule",
            "content": {
              "text": "### Applications\n- **`apps/playground`** - Full-featured demo app showcasing all capabilities\n- **`apps/minimal`** - Simple integration example\n- **`apps/essentia-demo`** - Audio analysis demonstrations",
              "originalHeader": "Repository Overview"
            },
            "metadata": {
              "strength": "SHOULD",
              "format": "Paragraph",
              "line_start": 15,
              "line_end": 19
            }
          },
          {
            "id": "rule_4",
            "type": "rule",
            "content": {
              "text": "Standard: **iPhone 16 Pro Max** — use `yarn setup:ios-simulator` for consistent setup.",
